MEXICO: Mexico stocks soar at close, surpass 3,400 pts.Mexico stocks soar at close, surpass 3,400 pts.Mexican stocks soared near the close of Tuesday's trading session, overtaking resistance at 3,400 points on their way to a new record close.The IPC index of blue-chip stocks was up 77.12 points or 2.32 percent to 3,401.79 at the close of trade, although the final total had yet to calculated.On Friday the bolsa index set a record close of 3,361.39 points.-- Dan Trotta, Mexico City newsroom, (525) 728-9507